<h1>Nag-ooperasyong tropa ng 62nd IB, binulabog ng BHB</h1>
<p>Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-03-12T96:00:00-04:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: None</p>
<p>Description: Binulabog ng mga Pulang mandirigma ng Bagong Hukbong Bayan (BHB)-Central Negros ang nag-ooperasyong tropa ng 62nd IB sa sityo Batang-batangan, Barangay Bucalan, Canlaon City, Negros Oriental noong Mar</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/northern-samar-armed-action-1024x502.jpeg">northern-samar-armed-action-1024x502.jpeg</a>']</p>
